name: Big Bad Superfight! Character Book
description:
Ready? FIGHT!!!

Get acquainted with the 30 characters of Big Bad Superfight!  Character profiles, stats, training methods and more are all packed in this 40-paged book of colorful characters.

Each book includes a 6"x9" character roster mini print, two 4"x5" postcards and a 3"x5" sheet of 11 die-cut stickers.

All items printed in the USA.

name: SAMSON 6x6 CANVAS PRINT
description:
"READY!"

Hailing from the TriStar Titan gym, Samson is a power puncher that loves going toe-to-toe with a tough opponent.  With heavy hands and a strong will he enters Superfight! to prove he’s not only the gym’s number one boxer but also show the world the power of Thunder Boxing.

The 6" x6" print is printed with fade resistant UV archival inks on a waterproof cotton canvas and hand-stretched over an anti-warping wooden frame.  Wall mount included.

name: BRICK 6x6 CANVAS PRINT
description:
"Let's go, punk."

Constantly in trouble with the law Brick is a well-known rabble-rouser.  He enters Superfight! to get revenge on Whiskers for catching him and putting him in jail.  In jail he upgraded his Rockhouse 26 style into the Rockhouse 52 style.  Now out for revenge he’s twice as strong and twice as dangerous.

The 6" x6" print is printed with fade resistant UV archival inks on a waterproof cotton canvas and hand-stretched over an anti-warping wooden frame.  Wall mount included.

name: WHISKERS 6x6 CANVAS PRINT
description:
"Stop right there!"

When whiskers was nine years old she was jumped by a group of ruffians and robbed of her grape lollipop.  Since then she’s dedicated her life to stopping crime and catching criminals.  She wears purple because of the grape lollipop that was stolen from her.

The 6" x6" print is printed with fade resistant UV archival inks on a waterproof cotton canvas and hand-stretched over an anti-warping wooden frame.  Wall mount included.

name: G.G. 6x6 CANVAS PRINT
description:
"Follow the rules!"

G.G.(Golden Gladiator) is the current champion of the NRRWF(New Ready Ring Wrestling Federaton.  A true technician he uses the many rules to his advantage in any and every way to assure victory.

The 6" x6" print is printed with fade resistant UV archival inks on a waterproof cotton canvas and hand-stretched over an anti-warping wooden frame.  Wall mount included.

name: CARROT 6x6 CANVAS PRINT
description:
"Let's be friends!"

No one has ever seen the real face of Carrot but they love her anyways.  Her bright energy and happy spirit have given her millions of fans called “Carrotines”.  Now the number one tv superstar sensation she wants everyone to like her!  Even the person she knocked off the number one spot: Boundy.

The 6" x6" print is printed with fade resistant UV archival inks on a waterproof cotton canvas and hand-stretched over an anti-warping wooden frame.  Wall mount included.

name: MUDMODE 6x6 CANVAS PRINT
description:
"MARSHMELLOWS!"

Mudmode and his Mudmen were enjoying a peaceful evening of roasting marshmellows until Bluebeard the Pirate crashed his ship into the island.  The fire went out and the marshmellows were ruined!
Mudmode and his tribe used the wood of the ship to start up the fire again.  Bluebeard didn’t approve.

The 6" x6" print is printed with fade resistant UV archival inks on a waterproof cotton canvas and hand-stretched over an anti-warping wooden frame.  Wall mount included.
